Name: Yes, Chef!
Title: The Pursuit of Perfection
Desc: The chefs make a dish worthy of a high-end restaurant, but won't be cooking the dish themselves.
LongDescription: The chefs make a dish worthy of a high-end restaurant that shows off their creativity and technique, but they won't be cooking these dishes themselves; will the chefs' high standards hinder their success or will their futures be left to fate?
